@title: Autumn Leaves
@artist: Joseph Kosma and Johnny Mercer
@tempo: Med Swing
@key: G Minor

#Section 1

The falling [Cm7]leaves drift by my [F7]window
The autumn [Bbmaj7]leaves of red and [Ebmaj7]gold
I see your [Amb57]lips, the summer [D7]kisses
The sunburned [Gm7]hands I used to [C7]hold
Since you went away the [Cm7]days grow long

#Section 2

And soon I'll [F7]hear old winter's song
But I miss you most of [Bbmaj7]all, my darling
When autumn [Amb57]leaves start to [Gm]fall

| [G7] |